sequenceDiagram
  actor Buyer
  participant UI as Buyer UI
  participant Cart as cart.php
  participant Checkout as checkout.php
  participant DAO as buyer_dao.php
  participant DB as MySQL DB
  participant Order as Orders Module

  Buyer->>UI: Add item to cart
  UI->>Cart: Save cart updates
  Cart->>DAO: updateCart()
  DAO->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE cart items

  Buyer->>UI: Proceed to checkout
  UI->>Checkout: Submit order request
  Checkout->>DAO: placeOrder()
  DAO->>DB: Create order + order items
  DAO-->>Order: order created
  Order-->>UI: Order confirmation